{"tid":1773094,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"連登垢病 嚴重影響戰情! ! ! !","createTime":"2019-12-07T07:57:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-07T08:15:59.000Z","uid":107157,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7a50c6db10f32021940fc2e63bb06936ae1b552f","tid":1773094,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T07:57:46.000Z","msg":"連登仔有個垢病就係<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不 斷 樹 敵</span></span><br />\n就連啲藍轉黃 無知淺黃 中立 既都要一一屌柒<br />\n最後搞到無任何人願意轉軚加入自己陣型。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />=黃 (和勇)<br />\ne.g. 正常連登仔<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />=淺黃 (無知淺黃) <br />\ne.g. 民建聯係咪黃絲我係咪要投佢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />=中立 (2邊屌)<br />\ne.g. 警暴要拉，示威者破壞都要拉<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/superman.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />=藍轉黃 (覺醒撚，人血饅頭撚)<br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />=藍 (狗)<br />\n<br />\n革命初期: <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n革命中期: (黃色經濟圈，民意支持)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/superman.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/superman.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n革命中後期:(連登仔力屌非黃同無知黃既人)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ne.g. 柒頭ming<br />\n革命後期: (人權法通過，區選大勝)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n總結: 總之佢撐我地，唔理佢想點我地都當佢地係黃。最多比個稱呼佢地，叫佢地「新黃絲」。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">切勿樹敵<br />\n比班政府狗<br />\n拉一派，打一派</span></span></div>"},{"pid":"de1d11602ac707a2beec122ac49b4055015e70ff","tid":1773094,"uid":2612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"